text: Simbarashe Gupo (born 7 July 1989) is a Zimbabwean first-class cricketer who plays for Mashonaland Eagles. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean cricketers Category:Mashonaland Eagles cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Kadoma, Zimbabwe
